Akfen Plans 500 MW Gas Power Plant on Mersin Site, Akin Says

-- B y   A l i   B e r a t   M e r i c
-- 
2011-10-04T13:29:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/akfen-plans-500-mw-gas-power-plant-on-mersin-site-akin-says.html
Akfen Holding AS (AKFEN)  plans to invest
about 250 million euros in a gas power plant on the land in
southern  Turkey  that it bought from the government for about $21
million at an auction, Chairman Hamdi Akin told reporters in
Ankara today after the sale.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ali Berat Meric in Ankara at 
 americ@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
